OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start in the east with
OL,6,Fsome rain but this clearing early
OL,7,Fmorning. The rest of the day will be
OL,8,Fmainly dry but a few scattered showers
OL,9,Fwill develop in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA largely dry and bright
OL,12,Fevening in the east but showers
OL,13,Fbecoming more frequent over Dumfries
OL,14,Fand Galloway. A mainly cloudy night
OL,15,Fwith further showers spreading east.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA bright start in the east,
OL,18,Fotherwise a mostly cloudy day with
OL,19,Fshowers or longer spells of rain.
OL,20,FBecoming drier from the west in the
OL,21,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
