OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FSunshine and heavy showers on
OL,7,FWednesday. A dry and sunny start to
OL,8,FThursday but cloud and patchy rain
OL,9,Fspreading east. Sunshine and showers
OL,10,Flikely on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
